“Don’t Trouble the Trouble. If you Trouble the Trouble, Trouble troubles you. I’m not the Trouble.. I’m the Truth!!!”  

As a dedication to him on his 56th Birthday (June 10, 1969), we appreciate Nandamuri Balakrishna for his contribution to Telugu Cinema. We also wish him success on his 100th film, Gautamiputra Satakarni.
